comments: ['The chat feature is incredibly broken. Multiple times I have had the "It\'s a match screen" but cannot actually message the person. If conversations do get started, most of the messages from the other person are missing, so we need to switch to personal messaging apps. So much for "personal safety". If you reach out to support, you will only get automated messages. Whatever NLP models they are using have terrible entity recognition and the automated message is 0% useful.', "It is a total waste of time and money. It does not matter if you have premium, you won't be receiving any matches at all (I had subscribed to the premium, still the same). It's like a window shopping app where you just keep scrolling and scrolling until you're satisfied without hoping to get anything. For once I thought this app could be genuine and I purchased the premium, but no, if all I had to do was left and right swipe people, I might have as well stayed on Tinder for free.", 'The UI is quite user friendly. But few things which can be improved on. 1. Message notification doesn\'t pop up a lot of times 2. Call notification doesn\'t pop up ever, plus call drops multiple times 3. Filter option doesn\'t work properly, for example if I choose age range 33-36, I still see people of age 23 4. Algo for common interest can be improved specially for best bees feed, I get best bees who want "Something Casual" while my preference is "Relationship"', 'I can not escape the feeling of a jacked up algorithm. One that puts people on the bottom despite their subscription in some sort of "lead with a carrot" business model. That or no one\'s on this app, and the app does not seem to want to take people who have not been on the app in months in the algorithm. Furthermore, there seems to be no quick, obvious, and easy way to end your subscription.', "I used the app for about one year and had a few decent dates out of it. However, as soon as my paid membership expired, literally overnight, I went from having zero people interested in me to 47, of course being prompted to go back to the paid version. Didn't change location or filters during that time, so obviously, they are manipulating the truth and the end user.", 'For an app that requires access to your location, you\'d think they\'d give you an accurate mileage estimate for people near you, but nope they can\'t be bothered to do that. Just saw someone who lives in the next state over from me and, according to Bumble, they\'re 85 miles away from me. However, when I enter the city on Google maps, it gives me a much more accurate mileage: 156 miles. That\'s a 71 mile difference, nearly double Bumble\'s "estimate."', 'The worst of all dating apps. Like Tinder, gives you options from ridiculous distances, especially if youre in rural areas. Most people are visitors from very far. The worst part is once youve swiped left on a potential match they are removed from your likes and you probably will never see them again."you\'ve missed a potential match" forever. Also they put the location at the bottom so you have to scroll the whole profile just to see the distance factor. Overall a very bad experience', "This app is ok but needs work. I canceled my premium. One of the big thing that must be added is letting me know when the last time a person logged on. That way I'm not wasting time on someone who hasn't logged on in a month. That's a waste of a swipe especially a super swipe. Also need to separate straight people from gay. As I have swiped on the wrong person and they get all offended. If these things were fixed I would keep logging in.", "I have emailed support multiple times about transferring my premium subscription from a previously deleted account to my new account and there has been absolutely no response from anyone in support. Unlike other dating apps that allow you to re-instate previously purchased subscriptions without having to email support (that doesn't respond to you anyway), Bumble just really need to sort its issues out.", "Terrible app! you have to pay for basic Things like just to see who liked you you can only see the people that complimented your profile and that's limited, You have to pay for everything like super swipes & to go back if you made a mistake. They took down one of my photos for going against community guide lines but it's a picture of me in a long dress no nudity nothing inappropriate. & whatever preferences youre allowed to choose (age and distance) doesn't narrow down the field", "Still an awful app, I've tried it multiple times and men never see their related matches. We get search results from 97 miles away from people who don't match our criteria. And you can tell even from the blurry images that you never see the people who actually do swipe on you. It's entirely designed to keep you swiping without any actual results. Don't waste your time", 'Waste of time and money, the location of people is totally hit and miss, when you do "match" with someone it is debatable if they are actually real or generated by the app to keep you interested. For an app that is meant to compliment your social circle/find people with similar interests and so on, no one actually talks. Might just stick with the old-fashioned way!', "All the other dating apps I get plenty of matches, but bumble is awful at what it's supposed to do. No matches, and because of the time limit to message you often miss the matches you do get. Pointless app and a waste of time. Edited, after the reply I received more likes than before after I left a review, strange, then they started to get less and Ive just realised the compliment feature has been removed. I think the free compliments were the only thing that made bumble worth using.", "Because you can't filter results by important categories like religion without paying, the app is essentially useless. You are forced to weed through thousands of profiles that aren't close to your value specifications. The profiles layout is also a mess, listing interests in a buckshot-style jumble where things like children, religion, age, location, etc are thrown into the mix randomly and you have to look around more to find it (those should be at the top of the list).", "I think it's more likely to get struck by lightning and win the lottery at the same time than get a match. It's way too easy to accidentally swipe left, and those swiped on can't come back, and the highlights cost 8 bucks each. Like, who even? Fix your app.", "What's the use of having the dating interface if you can't even contact/connect to a prospect without having to pay a bloody fee? And even then, even if you do want to spend on it, the chances of getting catfished is unbelievably high. The aspect of this side of the app is completely useless. I will give it props if you're using it for business networking purposes and works well if that is your ONLY objective. The dating interface is bonkers.", "it's very picky and decisive wanting you to spend money just like any other app. they shouldn't just give the option free to connect with anyone but they should make a lot easier if you want to say hello or block or do what you would like explicit or not. there's filters for everything. just make it all around app that everybody can use. it's 2023 and this is the longest run on sentence I've ever done. but we all know what we're looking for in the beginning and in the end and who may b in middle", 'It\'s just as bad if not worse than Tinder surprisingly. Customer service is 0/10. I can\'t get a hold of any humans to discuss my problems, I\'ve sent at least 10 emails. I get photos randomly taken down because they "violate" community standards according to the algorithm. I\'ve purchased the lifetime membership twice and, like anyone, deleted and reinstalled the app many times, but now I dont have the lifetime membership, and they won\'t fix it. Summary: All dating apps suck.', 'Bait and switched into "subscription". If I wanted to continue after the 1 month trial I agreed to paid for, I would have chosen a less expensive package. I cancelled the subscription and contacted support 20 minutes after charged, I had to open a PayPal case. 2 weeks later Bumble hasnt responsed. Bait and switch auto-subscriptions are theft. Ive lost $60 to this "free" app and have zero dates to show for it, just "content sellers" posting their Instagram and onlyfans.', 'Totally wast of time & Money, I have not received positive responses from the opposite gender. The 30-minute spotlight feature, promising up to 10x matches, did not help. People seem less active, making it challenging to find potential matches. Considering trying other apps, Bumble has not been useful recently. I do not recommend it based on my recent experiences.', "Bumble is useless without a premium subscription. All filters except age & distance are now locked behind a paywall, so rooting through all the bad matches to find someone is a chore. You only get 24 hours to respond to a match, otherwise you have to pay to rematch. And if you accidentally swipe left on someone you do want to match with, you have to pay to undo it. If the woman matches but doesn't start chatting within 24 hours, (Something that happens A LOT) the match disappears completely.", "Not sure how I feel about it. So far I like how the verification process goes and the app runs smooth but been on it for 2 weeks with premium and not worth it. You don't really get as much people due to the fact that the premium is expensive and also the notification when you do get someone doesn't really appear on either the app notification or email. Also anyone you've liked you can't tell if they even seen the like. Definitely needs more work for the cost.", "I like this app, in my opinion it' s very nice but it's just ridiculously expensive. probably the most expensive app I've tried. so I subscribed in different app although I still use the free features on Bumble. Some things could be better. don't like the fact that only match girls can do first move, think that's silly. I've been on a date with a girl and she complained that men never say anything, then I said we can't, first move has to be from girl.", "When you pay to upgrade and it run out. I have found that when you get likes the system doesn't match you with them. I wants you to upgrade. They then timed out and their gone. Don't pay for the upgrade or you'll just have to delete your account like I did. It should be above all, about finding a connection.", 'Having a limit on likes per day isn\'t a bad idea, but this app\'s limit is almost cartoonish. I can\'t spend more than a few minutes per 24 hours swiping without being told I need to pay 3 WHOLE DOLLARS to keep going. It\'s asinine. On top of that, almost everything else is locked behind paywalls. Though I do like that you can list your pronouns without having to first pick "man or woman." But that\'s just basic decency, not a feature', "I've been on Bumble for a few weeks now. Ended up paying for the boost, matched with someone who, for their prompt, asked me to verify my photo. Prior to this I had tried probably 20 times to verify, and was never able to. Yes I tried photos with just myself. Mimicking the pose, hand gestures, and even location exactly, but couldn't verify. Now I'm stuck on the verification screen, I'm being ignored by the support team. 0/5", "To the pros: fairly clean & simple UI, tho a bit outdated. Cons: gps based search, meaning swiping endlessly tons of people in proximity, including tourists & people in the airport and there's no way to filter out. And you have to scroll all way down to find out person is living somewhere else or doesn't disclose. So looks like tinder at this point and more oriented towards finding one night stand nearby. Exhausting & very disappointing experience for me and after a long time trying it, I'm out", "So there is a subscription model for 21 dollars a month, but this subscription does not come with the ability to see who likes you. For that, you'd need ANOTHER subscription 13 dollars more expensive than the regular subscription. To unlock seeing who likes you, you have to pay 35 bucks a month. That's gotta be an accident, right? Why would this feature not be in the regular subscription?", "Don't buy the spot lights!!!! The app will self activate them and email support stopped trying to help! I tried just not being on for a couple days till subscription weekly one was added when I did log on it has already used it and times out! Yes I emailed them and they tried a couple time but stopped helping. Lost 5 so far. And they are not doing anything to help. Very disappointed in you guys. I'm done I've cancelled the subscription and not trying to get your help when you just blow it off.", "It's...ehhh. My issues are the inability to filter out poly/ENM profiles looking for unicorns, continuing to get likes from men when I am a lesbian, the constant message ads and empty notifications, and the high cost of premium. Been using it for a few months now, met one potential person but I'm demoralized. I won't renew my subscription.", 'I tried several times to get my picture verified, including taking a picture, posting it, and then without moving, taking the same picture in the verify area. They still said I could not be verified. I contacted customer service about it, and my app got stuck on the verify photo page and would not leave that page. I then contacted customer service two more times about it and still stuck. It would be nice to at least be able to try the app out.', "Well developed but core functionality is behind a paywall, and there's no incentive to pay for an app that feels dead. Honestly it looks great but actually seeing who has matched you is behind a pricy paywall, so it's a dice roll as to whether two people see each other, and this makes the limited ability to like people (an otherwise good feature) greatly lower the ceiling on chances of matching. People have moved onto other apps.", 'The app needs work on how it recognizes and interacts with phone media. It\'s difficult to get it to recognize videos & it has double standards when it comes to photos and videos. The app allows the most pixelated pictures you\'ll ever see; however, it won\'t let me upload perfectly fine videos due to "low quality" (they\'re not), wrong dimensions (huh?), or not being shot on my phone (really?). So far, it\'s not very user-friendly.', "Swear this app is a con. I have 9 so say 'matches waiting for me'. I just used a boost and spent the full 30 minutes swiping to see if I would get anywhere with any of them (get rid of or properly match with them) and I didn't come across a single one of these people. It is so blatantly a scam just to make people feel like they have no option but to pay to see more etc etc...", "The customer service for Bumble is absolutely terrible!! I have contacted them over 10 times in a two week span and Bumble has not replied to ANY of my inquiries. My account is stuck on photo verification and I cannot access any othet part of my account. I am currently paying for the Premium option as well. Don't use this app - they dont care about you at all.", "Bought premium (little under $9/wk because it was on sale). Was good at first but right now it's not letting me view profiles of people who have liked me (I can see their picture but when I click on them a blank square comes up instead of their profile). Literally the only reason I bought premium was so I could see people who liked me, so it's very frustrating that the feature stopped working. Hopefully it will work again soon. Edit: also not letting me send or view messages right now. :/", 'Very good idea but poor efficiency; is a pity that girls have only 24 hrs to establish a contact... Also, you should put more filters: for example: eyes color, hair color, etc., and stablish options to search by that criteria; for exemple, if I only want to meet people without kids or blonde girls or short (or tall) girls, be able to find those persons easily.', "The premium option is nice, maybe a little expensive for what you get. My issue is that with the premium subscription you run out of people within your filters. But if you're subscription ends you will run out of likes before you run out of people within your filters. Things don't add up properly.", "Even after having premium it doesn't let's text to someone who liked my profile. It clearly showed in best bees match. But it didn't let me text. What a pathetic app. They just want you to keep browsing and keep paying for super swipes or compliments even after buying premium. You will get nothing here. I think they just got some profiles when they launched the app. Might be no longer active because this app doesn't let people text even after liking from both sides.", "Don't recommend, I submitted seven verification photos exactly the way my profile poster was & when I tried to get customer support I've gotten zero response back other than them saying they verified who I am but to try to keep verifying my picture that matches. I paid for the week premium & the app is still stuck in the verification process & will not let me move forward. & they're still trying to charge me of subscription fee. The email I get back from customer service is a auto generated"]

title: Hundeo: Puppy & Dog Training
description:
üê∂ Dog & Puppy Training Made Easy üêï
Don't have a dog trainer or puppy training school with you right now? No problem! Hundeo offers you step-by-step video instructions on the most important topics that a digital dog obedience school can offer you in your pocket. We guide you from puppy to senior with the right content.

300+ Tricks, Games, Recipes and Courses.
Discover a wide range of tricks, games, and recipes for dogs. Get inspiration for your next training session and have fun together. In this app, you can find for example these course topics: Basic Commands, Puppy Basics (Walking the Pup, Potty House Training, Bite inhibition, Puppy Nutrition, Puppy Games, Puppy Commands), Leash Training, Recall Masterclass, How to ignore other dogs on walks, How to behave during a visit, Clicker Course, Dog Impulse control Guide, Health Check at Home, Raw Food Diet, Muzzle Trainer, Calm at Office, New Year's Eve Training, Stop your dog from eating random things, Stop Barking Trainer or Stay Alone Course for Dogs.

Step by Step to Your Goal
We guide you to your goal with our interactive video tutorials.
The tutorials are designed so that you can be successful with just 5 minutes of training a day. It reminds you of your training and when you train successfully, you get a great trophy for your virtual trophy case. In addition to dog training methods, you will also find great activities in the form of pet games and recipes.

Anytime, Anywhere - At Your Own Pace
Out in the park or garden with no reception? No problem. You can download content and use it offline.

New Daily
Daily free quizzes, tricks, games, recipes and courses carefully selected for you. Tailored to you and your breed. (We have 285 dog breeds like Labrador, French Bulldog, Pug, Doberman, Chihuahua)

Playfully to Success
To keep you motivated, you get new challenges every day and earn flames and trophies. 

Individual Profile
Create a profile for your puppy, dog, or even multiple pets and keep track of what you have accomplished and what you still need to practice.

Connect With Others
Have you learned some cool dog or puppy tricks and want to compare yourself with others? Invite your friends or other members of our community to compare your achievements and watch videos of other dogs and puppies.

Your Favorites
Keep track and create your own favorites list for easy access.

Clicker and Whistle Always With You
With a clicker, you always have the right tone with you. A clicker is the most efficient way to teach your puppy tricks and exercises.

Trusted
This app was developed in collaboration with professional dog experts and pet trainers. You can be sure that the exercises will really help you.

Support
If you have any questions about Hundeo or your account, please contact our customer support: support@hundeo.com

Hundeo Plus Membership
To unlock all the features, you can upgrade to ‚Äòhundeo Plus‚Äô and choose between the following subscriptions:
1 month
1 year

Terms and Conditions: https://www.hundeo.com/en/toc/
Privacy policy: https://www.hundeo.com/en/contact/data-protection/

comments: ["The app is pretty good and easy to work around. My only problem is that I have to be on a subscription or premium plan in order to access most of the stuff. People who go to apps for dog training don't really have the money, so they're not going to be able to go on to the premium plan to get access to most of the app. Other than that, it's a good app", "For weeks under maintenance, no training plans available Update: I was not using an old version but I have Adguard on my phone. Seems like the app does not work if it's routed through Adguard...", "I honestly enjoy this training tips it's extremely helpful to me .", 'easy to follow! works well', 'This looks like a really cool app, and I was very excited to use it with my twin cavapoo puppies. But I was dismayed that after I created an account it said that there were only 7 days of a free trial and then I would have to pay for the app and would be automatically billed for it. Beyond not impressed with this bait and switch for what is advertised as a free app. I deleted my account immediately, and I better not be charged in a week.', "I just downloaded & has all the selections of different trainings, tips & tricks. looks like alot of information needed ..HOWEVER, I am needing something to be done QUICK...instead of learning one tip or trick at a time.. it wants to give me ONE lesson one day at a time...I have a dog with separation anxiety & will not stop barking.. barks all night & throughout the day at times.PLEAAE HELP.... I'm still trying other apps as well for the dog barking..whistling apps etc.. I can't afford the prem", 'fun and easy!', "Good app but my dog won't listen to me when I teach her high-five she only listen to me when it's paw or games,‚òπÔ∏è", 'Epic I just downloaded I tryed to get her to lie down but she just looked down but well work on it.', "Not Free at all!!! Advertised as free but the only 'free' part is an introduction to each lesson, the introduction only tells you what you will get out of that lesson and gives no advice at all. Don't waste your time unless you want to pay.", 'I tried it with my dog and definitely got results, the tricks and games are great fun for my doggy and honestly cheap for a year of home-training!', 'I love the great video collection. It is also good that there are not only educational videos but also about dog health.', 'Simple, easy to follow tips and tutorials. Helped me finally to get my puppy to sit and control those impulses!', "so far the app is very helpful, Roxie has already picked up on 2 new tricks! She's such a smart little girl!", 'Good free version', 'Very good and helpful I have a young dog and have long been looking for a solution that helps. I really like the step-by-step video tutorials.', 'wow it taught my dog to stay when I went some where yet he has separation anxiety wow thanks', 'it really helped me trane my dog not that good, but it is not the app it is the dogü•∞', 'Amazing app should use for sure only thing you need to pay it would be amazimg to gave it for free for some people it would be really useful', "my dog is a puppy and she doesn't now any tricks so I need help", 'tried free version for 7 days, forgot about it and they charged me not even month but for 1 year. Looks like scum.', 'Great for teach dogs tricks,and great recipes so over all brilliant app(my fav trick was little heart‚ô°‚ô°)', "Very nice app but one thing I don't like that is there is not Indian spitz bread option.I hope you will add it.", "DO NOT DOWNLOAD. THE APP DOESN'T WORK MOST OF THE TIME. ONCE YOU SUBSCRIBE YOU CAN'T CANCEL IT. IT'LL CHARGE YOU EVERY MOUTH AND THERE IS NO WAY TO GET OUT OF IT.", 'I recommend this app because it teaches your dog commands that you want them to listen to and it also help my dog sit shake and pound it which is a good thing', "Couldn't even get started. Just got to the setup your account and even after I did, didn't move on to the next stage.", 'The right thing for me as a dog owner Very well-developed app for dog owners. A well done app. I like it.', 'Installed in German . Could not change to English Language', "anyway we can get Great Pyrenees tips and tricks?!? found my lab, river, profile but can't set up my charlie bears just yet bc there isn't a bread set up for him yet.", 'wonderful app! Thank you so much, it taught my dog, Doc, how to stay', 'It has amazing trick ideas and amazing healthy recipes for your dog üê∂üêïüê©üê∂üêïüê©üêïüê∂', 'so good helps my dog learn so many new things', "It's nice but there was no breed option for English shepherd i hope you add that someday", 'Not able to login. Some error popping up', 'I know this is The only review but trust me,this is The Best app ever! My dog learned so much tricks from there!üòªüòª‚ù§Ô∏è\u200dü©π', 'The app looks good , i only gave it 4 stars because I have not used the training methods on my 4 dogs yet but I will try it tomorrow.', "Save yourself some money. title: Dog Scanner: Breed Recognition
description: The Dog Scanner app will identify your dog's breed reliably in just a few seconds! Besides taking a picture, you can also record a video or upload an image from your gallery. Got a mixed breed? No problem, the Dog Scanner app also recognizes mixed breeds! We provide you with detailed data and interesting facts about the different breeds of your mixed breed dog. No dog around? Doesn‚Äôt matter! The Dog Scanner app also recognizes humans: Simply scan yourself, your friends, your family or the people around you and find out which dogs you resemble the most! ------ NEW! Become a part of our Dog Scanner community! Share your results and compare them to the results of the community! Upload pictures of your favorite dog to our Social Feed and share them with other dog lovers! Have a look at the profiles and photos of other users, like and comment on posts from our dog community and filter them by date or popularity! Additionally, you can easily share your posts with your friends by simply sending a picture directly from the Dog Scanner app. ------ NEW! Catch all dog breeds and become an expert! Catch all the dog breeds with our Gamification feature ‚Äì just like in Pok√©mon Go! Master the challenges, earn virtual treats and become a true dog expert! Compete with your friends or users from the community and climb to the top of our ranking list! ------ All dog breeds in the Dog Scanner app! The Dog Scanner app currently identifies more than 370 different dog breeds, including all breeds officially recognized by the F√©d√©ration Cynologique Internationale (FCI) and even some more! Our comprehensive database with information and pictures of all dog breeds (including the unofficial ones) can also be accessed completely without scanning! Give us feedback on the Dog Scanner app! Let us know if the dog‚Äôs breed has been correctly identified. If not, you will get useful tips to improve your own results. If you also indicate which dog breed is in the picture, you help us to enhance our software since the app automatically learns how to provide even more accurate outcomes. Also suggest or vote for (unofficial) dog breeds that you want us to add to the app in the future! Get your premium upgrade! With our premium version, the app will no longer show ads and your results will be available faster. Furthermore, you can now choose whether your dog breeds should be recognized rather quickly or with higher accuracy. With the premium version, scanning dogs is also possible in offline mode, so you no longer need an active internet connection to identify their breeds. With the optional in-app purchase of our premium version, you will also help to support this app. ------ Find us on social media! On our social media channels we provide you with the most beautiful dog pictures from the community. You will also find many interesting facts about man's best friend. Furthermore, we will keep you updated on all new added features of the Dog Scanner app in the future. * Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dogscanner_app * Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DogScannerApp * Twitter: https://twitter.com/dogscanner_app ------ Just give it a shot! Dog recognition as easy as it gets! Despite the small app size you will get all features and be able to identify a dog‚Äôs breed or get access to our extensive database at any time! Before you consider getting an expensive DNA test, simply scan your dog with the app and the dog breed will automatically be determined within seconds! Download the Dog Scanner app now!
summary: See a dog, but don't know its breed? Just take a picture and find out!

comments: ["The app itself is not bad as a bit of fun, although suspect it isn't very accurate with mixed breeds. The number of ads makes it unusable though, as there seems to be one every 20 seconds and if you close one of the small ads, a full page one immediately appears. I may have purchased the ad free version if I had a chance to try the app for a bit longer, but am not prepared to watch that many ads just to decide if I like it.", "To say the ads are intrusive is an understatement. Every action you take gets an ad and the interface is similar to those websites that have 30 download now buttons trying to get you to download a virus. The TikTok ad is app-breaking. It is unskippable with no X to click. Even opening it still takes you back to the ad. There's no way around it but to exit the app. I did manage to get one picture in and it identified the breed incorrectly. Why would they think we'd pay for a pro version? 0/5. ;(", "I got the perfect shot and it correctly identified the dachshund in my dog. It all just depends on the perfect shot (all you have to do is just take a side picture of your dog looking at you helps). It just should lower the analysis time and have a better accuracy when people take pictures of the owners dogs. But I love it even if they didn't do that.", "actually surprised me! sometimes it fails to identify a common breed but then somehow it manages to CORRECTLY dentify random cross breeds. obviously the picture will play a part in how accurate the results are, but even a perfect pic might not get the right result cuz obviously identifying a breed by a pic alone isn't an exact science and one dogs can look like one think but be 100% proven to be something completely different, appearances can be misleading. cool app though", "I would definitely recommend this app. Out of all of the apps I tried, this one was bang on identifying a 4 week old puppy we rescued. the accuracy isn't 100% but pretty damn close. For anyone using this app, make sure you use more than one picture to see how many times it recognizes a specific breed, and then do your research. This is a great app to use to give you a lead on a breed, and the rest is up to you.", "Not sure to give it 2 or 3 stars. They did well to get 1m downloads so respect for that because it's main functionality which is the scan is average at best. They even openly admit on the app that the top 1 accuracy is 71%. This is a pretty bad result. If you like bells and whistles then this app is for you. If you would like to get proper identification - there are better apps around.", "1-27-21 App problems have been fixed. Great job! Update 9/27/20-Developer updated app. When scanning photo(s) from gallery the app no longer works properly but constantly flips back into camera mode. Unfortunate. From 5 to 1 star and deleting app. Will check back periodically to see if it's fixed. 7/31/20-So far, a truly wonderful and innovative app. I'm really enjoying it.", "Fun and pretty accurate readings based on a photo, or many different photos together to cover all bases. It was right on on my dogs and has a lot of info on specific breeds. I scanned many different photos of my dogs and it gave me the right answer with details on breed, or breeds. Very cool and fun. I was glued for over an hour playing around with this app. I don't think I'll delete it yet.", "This isn't a bad app at all. I've only used it for about four of my assorted mongrels so far, but it knew my hairy Bulgarian dog was a mix of various Eastern European shepherds. I don't know her origins, but the dogs it suggested seemed pretty close. Plausible enough for passing curiosity, anyway. I wouldn't want to settle an argument with it, but it's a bit of fun.", "Its something different and some what funny. But very unreliable. So unreliable that I am willing to bet it get's the dog breed every time unless ypu owm a pure bred. Again I am not hating the app or developers. Hopefully they can creat default ways to take pictures this way it is more accurate. Especially when considering am entire skeletal structure in a picture.", "the free version is nearly impossible to use bc the amount of ads. I mean, I've never seen anything like it. Waaaaaaaayyyy too many ads. pretty much every 3 click activates the same Temu ad for a washing machine ü´§", "I love it! I've been waiting to find something like this for years It's pretty spot on. I think it's cool that it can recognize mix breeds. I can't say for sure how accurate it is because my dogs are a mix of at least 2 but probably 3 or 4 different breeds, but the app results agree almost perfectly with our best guesses for both dogs, so i think it's great.", 'Absolutely awesome and how do you do it? I was very easily able to scan several dogs in our family (must sit still 5 seconds) with the app. The answer is perfect especially for Heinz 57 and somewhat mixed breeds. It gives a breakdown in percentages with sample photos to support their analysis. Suggest you take a FULL profile scan and not facial close up. Highly recommend this app!!!', "Pretty cool app. Just wanted ideas of what my dog could be mixed with as she looks like a larger version of a heeler. The only negative is the intensity of the ads. I'm fine with free apps showing ad banners, or occasionally a short ad, but press ANY button and you're stuck with a 30s ad video AND the post-ad promotional poster that makes you wait to press the 'x'. Good for a one time use it if you have patience, or probably if you pay", "I kept being interrupted by ads, and when I finally reached Dog Scan, there was nothing...NOTHING to show me how to use it!!!. It also crashed 3 times while I was on there. Don't bother with this app, its annoying and VERY frustrating!!!üò°üò°üò°", 'If you give it a reasonable photograph, it does seem to come up with reasonable matches. I tested three mixed breed adult dogs of unknown origin, but from the same litter. One of the three looks different from the other two. The app gave me the same sorts of answers for each dog. Dutch shepherd. I tested multiple photographs. The variation was not as great as I expected it to be.', "It's a good idea, but it's not accurate; It seems like developers are on the right path as far as using images submitted and asking users to correct what breed the scanned dog actually is for future recognition abilities of this app.... but it has never been right :/ I tried multiple dogs that I know.", "Could be useful to rescue groups and shelters. Best results when using a full view picture without much else in the photo. Not useful for some mixed breeds. Others have provided good feedback. I've tested some shelter dogs, comparing their guess to the tool suggestion. Many times I've agreed with the app over the shelter guess.", "The app is pretty good so far. The only time I can say for a fact it was wrong was when I scanned my rat terrier. She's a runt and sickly, so she looks more like a chihuahua. It scanned her as that, but it's a common mistake, so not one that surprised me. Aside from that, it gave me good insight on what my other dogs might be. Only issue is that the video ads can be intrusive. Went from one every 10min to 3 in a minute.", 'I have 2 poodles. One everyone thinks is not a poodle due to the texture of her hair. The scanner guessed both breeds correctly. I see complaints about the ads but it comes with the territory of a free app. Stop complaining or pay for the premium version.', "Dogs don't like loud sudden ad sounds in their face while getting a photo taken. These adds are full-screen and can't be backed out of. Unexpected startling ad sounds is not too smart for a pet friendly app.", "I had an incredibly loud and intrusive ad and it had no obvious X or mute, pressing what looked like an escape route forcefully opened my app store, once I went back to the app, the advertisement was still stuck on my screen, now it had an X and I pressed it, but it took me right back to the store again. Double kill. I don't think I trust this app and I'm deleting this immediately, it couldn't correctly identify my dog either.", "This app is pretty cool not to sure how accurate these kind really are. I took a picture of one of our dogs and got my friend in the picture and it kind of confused the app so it gave me an idea to take a picture just of my friend & the result was partly correct when it said human the very funny thing was it said the larger percentage was Great Dane. We laughed so hard. I still smile when I think about it. They do say sometimes we tend to resemble each other-thing is we don't have a Great Dane.", 'I have three foster puppies from the same litter, all were totally different. Also, took different pictures with same outcome. Different breed, every time.  Also took another picture of my dog (we had a dna test on him) again with different results that were completely different. It‚Äôs a good thing the app is free.', "It doesn't seem very accurate because I scanned my dog at three different angles and I got three different results and two of the same angle and two different results and not one of the breeds, out of all the five times I got results, did any of the results have one of the same as the others. So I couldn't even get a good guestimate.", 'I was impressed. scanner is most impressive. was able to get clear and focused images of dog scanned dog three times and he was identified as the same breed each time and the percent of account increased each time until 98%. Yes GREAT APP. üëç', "It's so cute! But besides that, it's fairly accurate so long as you do several photos from different angles. Sometimes depending on the features that certain breeds have, a weird angle could change the entire results.", 'Great fun! Used this app on my "pavement special" rescued dogs and came up with some interesting results. Not that accurate, but I won\'t hold that against this app as dogs can be difficult to identify, especially if they are bouncing around when you try to scan them - something the app manages to do well. Like I said great fun, informative on breeds and I enjoy using it.', "The app has been correct. I clicked incorrect on one of them because the husky breed was off but that's not a surprise because the breeds are so closely linked. a second scan of the same dog with body without the face came up with the closer mix. I'm very impressed and happy with the results. I also love the info that comes with the breed.", 'As someone else said it\'s good for entertainment value. App said my purebred Mastiff (rescued retired breeder) was Mixed breed and gave FOUR different breeds, most of them pretty off. Apparently my other 2 rescues are both Australian Kelpies, one of them a purebred - don\'t think so. [EDIT: have to eat my words - I searched black/tan kelpies and my "purebred" rly matches the look!] Using the app was nice enough (except for the ad every single time). It just doesn\'t have superb accuracy. Yet?', "it's kinda fun. I'm not sure I would pay for the app but it's fun to scan my dogs and see what it comes up with. I believe it scans the dog then runs the photo through its database of pictures and compares it to them. it pulls out the ones that look most like the dog depending on the angle of the scan you did. The first scan I did of my 3mth old puppy seemed pretty accurate. I will be trying my other dogs too. It also has a cat scanner option.", "I've only just downloaded this, but it correctly figured out the breeds of all three of my dogs, even from images where they weren't facing the camera, and figured out that my cat was, in fact, a cat when I tried to trick it. Now, none of those would be hard for a human to figure out, but I am genuinely impressed an app could manage it.", '4 and a half stars Nifty little app. I love animals, especially dogs, so I can defnitely see how having dog scanner will come in handy. Whenever hanging out with family and/or friends you can turn it into a fun game. Knowing dogs as well as I do I can see myself winning a lot, lol. Not only do you have the fun factor of playing a game, its an educational tool as well.', "Love, LOVE, L-O-V-E this app. and, I haven't even had it for 24 hours! I have been using a similar app, for several months. Yet, so far, Dog Scanner is, Leaps & Bounds above the competition. I mean, you guys are...KILLING IT! Period. I purchased the premium version of Dog Scanner. Main reason was to eliminate Ads. (Thanks, Ads-No-More). I was, also, impressed by the amount of, factually accurate, breed specific info (contained-within-the app.) Kudos-to-You, Dog Scanner. Your product ROCKS!üòãüôÉüòú", "This app is interesting, and insightful. I've only tried it with my dog, which was an unknown mix of breeds until I used this app. Very fun and surprisingly accurate for how many poor angles and lightnings I used in the pictures. The ads in app are very small and do not get in the way of using the app (thank you!!)", "I tried 4 different photos of the same dog, all clear pictures that included his face. (The dog is a stray mutt that showed up.) Results varied widely. Side views of the head seemed to work best. It doesn't work that great with mixes, but is still helpful in that it can suggest possible breeds present in the ancestry of your mutt. Then you can google those breeds specifically to see more pictures. Easier than combing thru photos online, but not as good as asking your vet, is my opinion.", 'Just downloaded the app, from one I saw so far it seems excellent. Obviously ads all the time....normal. What I would like to see is improvement on detailed info..like weight range and longevity. For me this seems like an excellent app for people who see a dog they like and interested in getting one, so providing this kind of information would bring greater interest in your app.', "Awful app. Ads whenever you press anything, can't figure out how to close the ads, cluttered and too complicated. Waste of time.", "Highly Accurate - Don't listen to the naysayers. Often times when people get inaccurate results, they are using a bad picture with bad lighting. This app has accurately identified over 100+ breeds as I volunteer at an animal shelter and have used it to identify both purebred and mixed dogs. Whenever it got the breed wrong, changing the angle of the pic, adding better lighting and finessing the overall picture - resulted in a correct identification of the mutt at hand. Enjoy! A great app indeed!!", 'Really cool idea for an app. One thing that would make the results higher quality would be to allow users to upload multiple photos from different positions, then run each photo through the service and average the results.']

comments: ["This app is pretty expensive. I also found it weird that some messages seem to be auto-generated because they aren't appropriate replies. The messages did not address things that we were discussing. And one more thing, I am not keen on subscribing monthly where they auto-renew and auto-charge when you ran out of credits. My credit cards and/or debit cards should only be charged whenever I want to purchase credits. I do not want a regular subscription.", 'First, the subscription/credit is expensive. Second, it seems like the popular accounts are scams or computer-generated so you can purchase more credits. Observe the messages/mails you receive and also the pictures Third, a chat is charged one credit but the longer the message, it cost more credits. Reading an email alone costs 10 credits. Definitely not going to recommend this.', "nice app. just wish it were easier (less credits) to chat with people whom you have started communicating with...especially if you don't have a lot of money to buy credits. And beware I had several scammers contact me. Always fact check and do reverse image searches because no dating site can prevent scammers. And for some reason, men in China said they could not see my pictures on my profile. ??? What's up with that? The app makes you pay to message 'popular members'.", "Worthless. You pay monthly subscription ¬£33 plus on top of that you have to buy separately credit like 20 credit that u can send only 2 texts with it, with 20 cradits you can send 2 texts only, and that 20 credits cost ¬£22 so you can't even have normal conversation with the person. Plus everyone is in USA I personally didn't see no 1 from UK. Such a waste of time and money", "it is not a good site asked for a membership cancellation on 10/08/23 via email as I no longer want to be a member a yet they continued to ignore my request so they can continue to take my money. They have continued to send match email notifications though. They have so called customers support on WhatsApp messenger and email but no reply from any of them. it's over priced for what it is. i advise anyone not to us this app", "It's very,very,verrrrry√Ωyy. Expensive.. ü•¥ü•¥ü•¥.... I never never never.. purchase here again... super expensive. The email you received from the person had an intention to you. You have to pay for it before you open. Before you reply. You have to pay, they have a limited credit in every purchase you want.. üôÑüôÑüôÑü•¥ü•¥ü•¥ and there is no free credit. Even if 5 credit only a day..", "You charge me as a monthly fee , yet when you run out of credits there is no access to anything on this site til you by more credits .. I like the site seems genuine . but way to dam expensive to get any kind of good convo going with some one .. there should be at least free text messages with someone that has been in a long conversation with .. it sucks you credit packages have to big of a gap between them .. make some more smaller packages .. and don't be so dam greedy ...", "The app is great but it was soo EXPENSIVE even you meet someone that interest you, the conversation is very limited, because you have to spend big amount of money to continue the conversation and to know the person, I DON'T RECOMMENDED THIS DATING SITE, they really not helping us to find that special someone, they just take advantage of our desire to find happiness, by milking money from us. Most importantly there are lots of fake profile, it say confirm profile but fake.", "I'm wondering why this app exists if not to scam people for money. Great concept of app, which could have been great if genuine with customers at heart. All profiles seem to be fake or some form of robotic/AI generated pictures, messaging and responses. It's useless if you don't pay for the exorbitant fees. Please don't waste your hard earned money on this app. The app's representatives responding here all seem defensive and very robotic responses with no human touch.", 'This app is incredibly expensive, with every single chat and letter costing a penny. I find it strange that some of the messages appear to be repeated or automatically generated.', 'Be very careful. I talked with some nice people on this site but avoid the "popular members". None of them are interested in an engaging conversation, only how many credits you can spend. They never really read your profile and even if your profile is blank they are still full of compliments. Every single "popular" member is the same.', "help centers states if your plan isn't enough & you want to upgrade then they would help with that. They didn't even want to refer it to a manager. No response from any messages except phone, Prices are very high. Seems to me many with free account wiill encourage more exspensive communication- emails, pics. They can get %of precent value- what other incentives do they recieve. So are there to create followers", "This is the worst site I've ever been on. Day1 I was overwhelmed by 200+ (canned messages) which initially is a plus until you realize to answer you have to pay $24.99 for 1000 coins. Each response depletes 60 coins, your money is gone in 16 replies. You should notice the patterns of responses regardless the language, * Short one sentence replies *Rushed to get you to cybersex *Never willing to go to text, FB, IG Don't waste your money, most likely paid people to keep you on the hook.", 'Everyone on this app is not real. Employees put fake profiles, and the fake people send you presents and videos, so you will buy credits to talk to them. I was scammed by several African scammed posing with fake pictures. Whatapp and Signal Communications were fake. The people I communicated with used the same questions and answers. They used the same romantic jargon.', "Everything is for paying subscribers . In the free version you can't send messages or email. So unless you're willing to pay for a subscription this app is not getting anyone a date. Useless app.", 'This app is a big scam..i search all the photos of a popular member who message me and i found out that their actually using other people pics from instagram,be careful dont talked to them and take not do not suncribed its too expensive and many of the user are fake so dont waste your time in this app..', "This app costs so much, if you have no money you can't connect to anyone and even if you pay for subscription you are only limited to your credits. This sucks.", "Please guys don't ever purchase here coins or even monthly cause this apps is really scam.i purchase for 1month 1,500 only a few msg i send then i need to paid again also the men there i really think and im sure they just pretending also but still they just want to make money from you.specially Philippines girl don't believe this apps they are just wanted your money.its very big lier guy there they will ask photo and then you paid a lot of coins...", "I don't think the people are real!!I just opened the app after registering and received messages from two girls immediately...!!!It doesn't Make any sense!!!", 'Obviously, the popular members are dummy accounts used by agents to lure you in spending more money in buying expensive credit points. In addition, I just recently loaded 20credits and I just checked on the email, it went down immediately to 5.', "Very Costly and secondly thing is even after having great chat with the girl/bot,they still say we haven't talked much.Finally I came up with an idea to share my number and email addresses so that we can chat outside the app but seems like they just want you to chat here to lose your coins on this app due to their ex is still following her so they can't trust anyone outside this app blah blah...and tons of excuses.I realised these people are prostitutes.Fraud app,just playing with our emotions.", 'This is scam, you must rename this into "Pay to Date" , or "Pay to meet" , everyone!!! this is not for meeting purpose but to income purpose you can read and send few message, but the succeding have price to pay.', "I'm quite sure this app is a scam ... It‚Äôs very expensive, and the people on here all look like models with professional photography and videos. The messages seem likebtheyvare all from bots. Please do not waste your money", 'Most of the "profiles" are simply bots, that\'s ridiculous. You spend a lot of money talking to them to find out its a big scam. Very sad the company feeds on people\'s loneliness. I\'ve tried to delete my account multiple times over the span of at least 6 weeks- nothing is happening, no response from customer service and the WhatsApp number given is none existent.But they keep taking money from my account every month, tho I have been using the app for a couple of days only before trying to delete!', "Sick and tired of mindless swiping and superficial connections? This might be the dating platform you're looking for. If you're ready to ditch the casual flings and dive headfirst into a meaningful relationship, it may be worth signing up. This app really helps me to find a mature men.", "Fake app. The men pictures look like models, and the conversations are too well thought out, plus it's TOO expensive. Trash!! Also, it won't let me delete my account.", 'Its too expensive that amount to pay just to send and receive messages it absurd. You need to make it free at least for users to enjoy it, even if you want to monitize it, it should be reasonable pls. Someone will lose lots of matches not cool', "I have read all other people's review, honestly there are 2 issues..exorbitant fees, and no exchange of contacts details.Why? In your view after how long must partners exchange contacts. Is it a deliberate way to delete contact details so that you keep members on your dating side to keep paying. Very dissapointed. Sadly it does not look like you plan to help the customers. Loneliness is indeed a crime. At least add free button to indicate you like the other person but you lack credits to respond", "Awfull. First time to use the app and upgraded my account for a month of 23‚Ç¨ . I thought that upgrade will give me the freedom to chat and use the app But got shook with other fees for credits deducted again from my account for 113‚Ç¨. I can't take it. I've emailed and i hope for a reply asap", 'Awful. All matches are coming from off shore for which I have no interest. There should be a setting for this. Additionally, the alleged Customer Service number is not available. And most profiles look like a hoax. And, the app wants money at every turn. Awful!!!!! I want to close my account... Now!!!', 'Worst app. Waste of money. Why I need to pay again and again whenever the credits get over. It would be better if you charge monthly and not for the credits.', "the video chat is not good you waste your credits and very expensive they charge by the minute and your credits go quick this site is expensive for credits and you have to wait months to get a better deal whoever designed this site is laughing all the way to the bank you are not going to meet any body here when you get to that point never happens they hide behind there phone or computer the mask is who they are I wouldn't bother spending your money you will not get a relationship these women", "For you to chat you have to subscribe. And the prices are way too expensive. You can only send one msg n you can't even read the reply from the other person. It's a scam", 'If you pay for a membership, you still need to pay to chat and read emails with credits. Too costly and some people are not real.', 'the app is very good but the subscription amount is just to much and if you subscribe for a month it takes only a few minutes chat and you will be told the subscription has finished', "I've just recently registered on this wonderful app but I can say that it's easy to use. From creating your profile to browsing potential matches, the site provides you with an advanced matching algorithm. I like it. Just reduce your pricing a bit.", "It would be a 5 but the cost is way to much ,I get the subscription that's fine ,but then you have to pay to actually speak to people,it's crazy expensive.sadly canceling my subscription", 'the website is good, but the costs are high. for someone who wants to find love but credit scheme is silly. just charge one monthly fee', "good app but high price to purchse credits, it is difficult,but mostly women's interested in chatting in the app only ,not interested to connect with the person even after telling,silly questions are repeating from the members,i don't know who are original/fake, because no one is ready to connect,it's very surprising & strang , question arises that app doing all these things,then there is no useful from this app.waste of time.", "way too many scams on here phony profiles set up by men better behind the females also the other ones that are verified and are popular members they cannot even prove himself so they got to be phony don't trust this site all the females get you to do the ones that are popular or to buy more credits they do not have to pay for their credits they just trying to get you to buy credits to make the date site more money do not trust I have gone as far as."]

title: Merge Dogs
description:
Merge your dogs, build the ultimate dog racing team and win the race!

Do you have what it takes to be the best dog racer out there? Start by getting small puppies, then upgrade them into bigger faster dogs and earn lots of money!

Features:
- Over 20 different dog breeds to discover including shiba inu, corgi, golden retriever, pug, french bulldog, chihuahua, poodle, beagle, dachshund, dalmatian, dobermann, rottweiler and lots more!
- Idle earnings. Gain coins even while you are away or offline.

Manage your team of super fast dogs. Start your dog racing team now and become a champion!
summary: Build your doggy team and win the race!

comments: ['The design of everything is very simple and cute. The animations and feel of it is very happy. You do have to wait, but the animations help for the wait time since the animation entertains you as you wait. A very fun game overall. Perfect for people who like achievin', "This game was fun at first but it starts playing you when your about the finish the game like not giving you your money and taking your good dogs and replacing them with bad ones ( for example there are 5 pages and I was on the husky on the 4th page and they replaced it with a dog from the fourth page) which may not seem like a big deal but the higher the dog the more epband money so replacing it so you get less and have to wait months for a new dog This game is just impractical don't waste time", "Starts off fun but after you gather a few dog species it becomes very difficult to move in to the next species. especially because the money you gather while the app is off is limited. Fun but has more potential. I've dropped it now.", 'Very addictive. As a dog person this game is perfect for me. If you are a dog person you should download Merge Dogs! The graphics are great. So many new types of dogs to collect. I have used the 2x speed. It is one of the best money makers in the game. The 5 star review has been earned. Download right now!', 'It\'s ok... a bit confusing at first figuring out what to do and what the purpose is of having the dogs run laps in circles... keep thinking they\'re going to get tired and get thirsty... thought it was going to be more like a "real merge three" game, not merge two or more. I do however enjoy "creating" the new dog species! it is original, but it needs improvements overall. gets repetitive and lacks incentive after awhile. but I think many people would like it with a clear explanation of what it is', "Really good game it gets kind of boring because it's just a loop you get a dog you merge the dog then again. I think it's a very good game though.", "I love everything but could get lil boring rarely adds don't have to pay money it's good üòä one thing though there is bugs like sometimes one of the dogs was tiny and hard to see maybe see what's wrong? I recommend the game though ;)", "This game is amazing! There are rarely ads, and the dogs are super cute! The only thing is that it gets boring sometimes but that's okay! PLEASE download this app!!!", "Alright, so, I really enjoyed this game at first. It was super fun, really cute, definitely addictive. However... I'm about halfway through the catalogue both for the grass track and the snow track, and now it's boring. It takes too long to get to the bigger dogs, since you only get two hours of away time. There's an upgrade for two more but... Do I wanna pay to still barely be able to buy two dogs at a higher tier? There just isn't enough to do to keep it fun. Good for a while tho!", "This game started out lots of fun and I was always excited to see all the new dogs you could unlock but as you get into the later stages, sometimes my best dogs are randomly deleted and replaced, I have been playing for a long while so it takes weeks and months to get a new dog but they keep getting replaced before I can get a new dog, it does it often and it's impossible to progress through the game at this point. It takes away from the cute aspects. Example; Lost my Samoyed for a Dalmatian.", 'This is a good mindless game to pass the time, it helped me fall asleep. A tutorial would have been nice, I played for days before I figured it to click on the dogs and rabbits. The look of the pit bull was disappointing. All the dogs are very happy looking except him. The devs had an opportunity to put the beautiful dogs in a positive light and they took a wrong turn with it. Last, I beat both levels in just over a week, more levels would be awesome. I am uninstalling for now.', 'okay. i love the colours and the art style used! they really compliment each other and make the game enjoyable. i REALLY like the ability to buy certain dogs as you level up!! that makes it a lot easier but still challenging enough to keep playing! one thing i would like would be the ability to purchase outfits for certain dogs, with in game watch to earn ads, and ingame cash from the dogs. overall this game is great ‚úåÔ∏è', "Addicting and fun, until the ads stopped working, except, of course, the ads that provide zero benefits, which also happen extremely often now. I tried restarting the app multiple times. No luck. Fix this soon or I will delete. I already had to skip a bunch of rewards that I can't get anymore because I could have gotten them by watching an ad. Not satisfied at all... :( UPDATE: They sort of fixed the issue. I can get a reward from a video once, then I need to restart the app, so 3 from 2 stars.", 'This game is great! So fun! When i downloaded it at first i was a bit skeptical thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs when i got pretty far in the game but i actually enjoy the way they set it up greatly! How you let the dogs run to collect more coins. Its creative and a good way to not run out as well as you dont have to buy coins or watch ads for them! üòÅ Love the game! Addicting, easy, and loads of fun!', "The game isn't really challenging for the mind. Buy a dog, for ever increasing prices, or wait for a free one. Let it run on the track to make money. Combine two of same to get another dog, of a higher level. That one will get you the same income as the two old dogs, only faster, so merging dogs is usually worth it. The rest (free dogs, 20% discount, double speed) is click bait, you get something and the designers earn money. But in the ent, it's surprisingly funny and addictive. I quite like it.", 'I love this game the only thing I wish they could improve is how long you have to merge the dogs. Anyways the whole rest of the game is great!üòä', 'This game is amazing and I love it. I stayed up late playing this game!! It is awesome!! I recommend it to whoever is looking at this. If you like offline games... This is for you! All you have to do to get rid of the ads is turn off your mobile data (if you have that) or turn off your interet! Then no ads. It does load, but dont worry. This is a 5 star rating!!! Love it so much. Again you can always get rid of the ads by turning off internet or mobile data. Anyway, thats my review! ü•∞üê∂üêïüêï\u200dü¶∫', 'MAGNIFIC DOG MERGE GAME üêï good work. Thank you! üê© I was about to finish the game, so I uninstall it to restart it, so much it is relaxing and awesome . üíï', "This game was fun but you need to add a tutorial for new player's but it does help me fall asleep.", "its a cute game, and the dogs models are adorable. it has a short, simple tutorial which is nice. I just don't like how long it takes to upgrade to the next dog. it's a slow-paced game compared to most idle games but that's not a horrible thing. the in-game purchases are also a bit overpriced. I love it as a time passer, but I'm uninstalling.", "It's a cute game but it just feels so plain and basic. At least in Merge Planes you could get boosters, etc for the track, and there was a leader board. I don't want to watch fifty million ads just to make my dogs go faster, etc. And they don't even go that fast with the ads. Plus, the ads don't always work. You need to do more to this otherwise boring game.", "It's a cute app, but is it fun? sort of, at your lowest stage it's fun and you merge but soon it becomes into a log on, collect reward, buy more dogs, close app, repeat. I do like that the ads aren't forced but I do watch them anyway. 1 video to double my 2 billion? sure why not. most people won't like this but I do like grind fest games. so it's cute and it's grindy, following the popular trend of merge apps. with not anything else thrown in to spice it up, that's about it.", "The cutest game I've played so far. The game is very simple and really good for destressing. Animation is cute, and I get excited every time I get a new dog. I'm unable to play ads though so I can't redeem other features. But overall the game is just really chill and enjoyable.", 'This is a great game. But I have a problem, my progress keeps getting lost! I was at the level were I unlocked the sheltie but I come back the next day and it is gone, i still unlocked it in the book of dogs but did not have it on the track. I probably wont get a reply or a bot reply I just hope that this problem gets fixed.', 'I wanted to like this game, but there are a few things that turned me off. First of which was the farther I got in the game, the speed in which the dogs speed around the track literally made me sick. Visually it was disturbing and maybe should come with a warning. The second thing is why is the pitbull the only vicious looking design. All the other breeds look super sweet and friendly. I think the designers are perpetuating an unfair bias.', 'Fun game, but a while ago(long time) i had much progress on the game when it randomly crashed and wouldnt open, this went on for a week until i gave up. When it finally let me play it deleted most of my progress. It is now crashing again and im thinking it will do what it did previously, nice app, but please fix it so it doesnt delete progress, or atleast let us save it somehow.(im on latest version so that cant be why.)', "This app is so so cute and fun!! But it has a bug that happened to me twice. I don't know how that happened but it was in the snow place that my fastest dog lost two times. So I have to use more money and it's so hard because of slower income because of the bug. And also the away time says I'll get my income for 4 hours when I don't use the app but it's just actually 4 minutes. I was supposed to earn at least a trillion in 4 hours but it just gives me 50 billion. It's a fun game though. = )", 'Stopped playing it last year because constant crashes made it impossible to play. Felt the urge to play it again and glad to see that the crashes have been fixed! Cute and fun way to pass the time!', "Thia game is an adorable idle merge game, there's enough factors that go into each dog that give the game more depth than expected, and I love that it has multiple worlds or zones that play at the same time. The only thing I think the game is lacking is a more solid active playing aspect, I'd like to see some kind of minigame alongside the idle aspects, but it's still a complete game that is worth your time.", "Like the game as a way to kill time. Got to Pom, and it looked like it was floating? Thought nothing of it and continued to play, only to find that when I got a 2nd Pom, they wouldn't merge. Closed the app and restarted - my 2nd Pom is going and the Pom I have has been taken off the track. This has happened twice now.", "I think that the game was very simple and easy. It was very short thought. You barley got any dogs and most other breeds can be left out. I know it is kinda tricky to find nonpopular breeds of dogs, but I still think it's great. To the game creaters, you should make one with cats and the different breeds also. I think the game was very cute and I enjoyed it.", "well.. I liked this game, it was fun to merge the lil doggos to get more doggos. BUT. After getting over half the doggos in the regular one and almost completing the snow one, the game continuously crashes. I open it and not even 2 seconds later it crashes. Not enough time for me to do anything. It's super frustrating because I'm just so close to finishing it. I put a lot of effort into this.", "It's an easy game to pass the time with. But a few too many ads for my liking. It's ok to have ads for bonus things like the 2x speed but i don't like that one automatically plays for 5 seconds when i close the buy-a-dog screen.", 'The music is greatüëç and very happy üòä! I love the dogs üêï ‚ù§ and they are very cute üòç! the racing is adorable ‚ù§!', "great game, I'm enjoying unlocking so many great breeds of dogs. the ads are a bit much but I'm not even mad considering you can use it for speeding up money, leveling up to a higher breed when using money, but it randomly comes up when you arent clicking anything that would start an ad and it gets quite annoy when an ad appears for no reason.", 'after a while you can no longer watch ads because the dogs are going so fast, so every time an ad tried to pop up, you have to watch your dogs run behind a loading screen for about 5-10 seconds.. I miss the "watch an ad to make them go 2x as fast!" or "watch an ad to get the next level of dog!" so yeah, the process is becoming a lot slower but I still love to poke the doggos. its actually quite addicting considering it gets laggy after a while', "Love it! Super cute and fun! However!!! It doesn't do a good job at conveying some things. Things like the X2 multiplier lasts 2 minutes and 30 seconds. And it doesn't tell you how much your max away is. All it tells you is that you'll get 2 more hours of max away if you pay them real cash money. A bit unnecessarily annoying.", 'I love the game so much it is a cute doggy game I love I how you can get different dogs my favorite so far that I have is my best one the dalmation. I love this game! Update) I would like a "Save" feature. I recently uninstalled (For storage and realized "oh fu-".) Reinstalled and lost my progress. If you could add a save feature so i can reload my work would be nice, If its already there then ;-;-', "Got months of playtime out of this. Simple idler with ROCK SOLID design. Art is adorable, control is intuitive, and lots of dogs means it last you a while. A few design elements raise its quality of life as time goes on: The quick-buy button (not real $) for the smallest dog eventually moves up the ladder as you unlock new dogs, so merge chains don't become impossibly long slogs. And you can always tap the dogs on your track for a little extra speed/cash. My new benchmark for merge-style games.", 'A Great Game! So much fun! At first when i downloaded it looked skeptical and confusing thinking about how hard it would be to get more dogs but when i got a bit far in the game, i actually enjoyed the way it was set up. Love the game, Addicting, easy and lots of funs.']

title: Panda Games: Pet Dog Life
description:
Welcome to the Pet Dog Home! Are you ready to begin a cozy house life with your dogs? Adopt dogs, take care of them and play with them!

ADOPT DIFFERENT DOGS
14 adorable dogs of different breeds and colors are waiting for you to adopt. Each dog has its own personality! Adopt your favorite dogs and live in the pet dog home with them! There are surprises in every corner of the cabin!

TAKE CARE OF PET DOGS
The dogs' day starts with a delicious breakfast! Add dog food, and feed them well! After playtime, give your dog a nice bubble bath! Don't forget to monitor their health and treat the sick ones!

DRESS UP CUTE DOGS
Now, open your closet and dress your dog in cute clothes! First, let's wear a cape for your dog and then pick a nice bib for it. Last, put on a cozy little hat for your dog! Done! Your dog looks even cutter now!

PLAY WITH DOGS
There are so many toys that you can play with your dogs: frisbee, swing, and more! Play with your dogs in any way you like at the pet dog home! This will bring you closer together. Try different fun mini-games and exercise your brain while playing!

Download Panda Games: Pet Dog Life and spend some fun time with your dogs in the pet house!

FEATURES:
- 14 cute dogs available for adoption;
- Feed, bathe, dress up and take care of your dogs;
- Explore the Pet Dog House: living room, bedroom and playhouse;
- Plenty of dog toys: tennis, swing and frisbee;
- Many fun mini-games to play with your dogs;
- Supports offline modeÔºÅ

About BabyBus
‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
At BabyBus, we dedicate ourselves to sparking kids' creativity, imagination and curiosity,and designing our products through the kids' perspective to help them explore the world on their own.

Now BabyBus offers a wide variety of products, videos and other educational content for over 400 million fans from ages 0-8 around the world! We have released over 200 children's educational apps, over 2500 episodes of nursery rhymes and animations of various themes spanning the Health, Language, Society, Science, Art and other fields.

‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
Contact us: ser@babybus.com
Visit us: http://www.babybus.com

WILD - The Fast-growing Hookup App for Adult Singles to Seeking Casual Encounters, FWB & Relationship! 

Wild is the Fastest way to meet & date with hot singles in New York, Los Angeles, Houston, Chicago, San Diego, Las Vegas, San Antonio, Phoenix, Philadelphia and other cities in the US! Forget other dating apps/sites, Wild is the only Free dating app you'll ever need! We have included all of your favorite features into one app and even more:

Free Chat - It's 100% FREE to chat with your matches.
Send unlimited Notes with anyone if you become a VIP.
Powerful Search Filter - You can look for Long-term Relationship, Hookup, Casual Encounters, and Friendship! No need to waste time on people with different intentions!

Anonymous - You can anonymously browse with just a private photo!

Real People - Date with real people! Over 65% of users are with verified photos.

Wild is not a pure hookup apps/sites but also a friend finder for adults. Whether you are seeking "Casual dating", "BBW dating", "Down to chat" or "Relationship dating", Wild can meet your needs. 

One-stop Dating App - No matter you are for straight, bisexual, lesbian or gay dating, we've got you covered!

Ready to have some fun? What are you waiting for? Download the OFFICIAL Wild Dating app and start browsing, chatting & dating for free now!
